earning, and a convenient integration\nwith the entire SageMaker suite allowing these trained models to be used in a\nproduction setting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2020 18:29:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 18:51:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-17"}
