all inside\n$r_{200}$ and that, by the time they reach $r_{500}$, most of them are already\nquenched.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Dec 2020 20:08:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
