icle are both\nhighly unlikely causes its observed spin state change. If true, this is the\nfirst case when the YORP effect has been detected for a tumbling body.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 07:15:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-16"}
